{
  "stem": "471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, by Schindler, we-- we knew we're going to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also, you could only-- to feed 1,000 people is not so simple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in other words, if we had additional-- they didn't-- the SS didn't give us anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if Schindler give something, he could give you a little bit only.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were still hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were still after the potato, or whatever you could find.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever, what, anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were still hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you assured one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You won't die from bullet, from getting a bullet in your head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you die, you would die from starvation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But actually, over there, you couldn't starve either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know, if this would go on longer, probably we would.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One fine day-- I have to skip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One fine day is-- is a rumor that Goth, they let him out from the prison.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he's going to walk by the factory with his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he said, Schindler, I'm going to be with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He has no authority or any power.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He was just let out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when he was let out, so he came to Brinnlitz, to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Probably, you know, because they found out he comes from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They found, in his apartment, all the way to the-- to the ceiling, liquor and-- and-- and cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the way, that's how much he had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A-- a-- a fortune.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, that's why they investigate him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From where you got that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had no bribe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you're suppose to SS, belongs to the government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the way he got-- and he got off.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
